Download logo Eritrean nationals in various Scandinavian cities contributed over 2 million 225 thousand Kroner in support of the activities of the Eritrean Communities.  According to the Eritrean Embassy nationals in Sweden contributed 1 million 500 thousand Kroner, nationals in Norway 530 thousand Kroner and nationals in Denmark 160 thousand Kroner. The nationals also expressed conviction to strengthen organizational capacity and unity as well as participation in national affairs. The Eritrean national committee in the Scandinavian countries commending the support extended by the nationals called for reinforced participation and contribution for a better outcome. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Ministry of Information, Eritrea.